==English==
===Pronunciation===
IPA: [[WEAE]] /ˈæk.tʃu.ə.li/

===Adverb===
#In act or [[in fact]]; [[really]]; [[in truth]]; [[positively]]

===Usage note===
In some [[Romance]] languages a word of similar spelling means "now"; e.g., Spanish "actualmente". This leads many non-native speakers of English to use "actually" when they mean "now".

===Synonyms===
*[[in reality]]
*[[literally]]
*[[really]]
*[[truthfully]]

